      <div xml:id="NA198-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu piṉceṉṟa cevili iṭaiccurattuk kaṇṭārkkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante encouraged HER who was unable to bear it when the marriage was delayed.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA198">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            cēyiṉ varūu matavali yāvuyarn</l>
<l>            tōmai nīṭiya kāṉiṭai yatta</l>
<l>            muṉṉā ḷumpark kaḻinta veṉmakaḷ</l>
<l><seg xml:id="1">kaṇpaṭa nīrāḻn taṉṟē tantai</seg>  <space quantity="2"></space>      <seg xml:id="2">aṉṉāy kaṇpaṭu pāṉṟaṉi raṉṟē</seg></l>
<l>            taṉṉū riṭavayiṟ ṟoḻuvē ṉuṇpal </l>
<l>            kōṭēn talku larumpiya titalai</l>
<l>            vāarn tilaṅkuvā leyiṟṟup polintatārc</l>
<l>            cilvaḷaip palkūn talaḷē yavaḷē</l>
<l>            maiyaṇa leruttiṉ muṉpiṟ ṟaṭakkai</l>
<l>            valvil lampi ṉeyyā vaṇmakiḻt </l>
<l>            tantai taṉṉū rituvē</l>
<l>            yīṉṟēṉ yāṉē polikanum peyarē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O strong man that comes from a distance, water sank so as to fill [my] eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">	[because of] my daughter who passed by over there yesterday</l>
<l rend="indent2">	on the road in the midst of the forest where Ōmai trees have grown long</l>
<l rend="indent2">	[and] Yām trees have become high.</l>
<l>I pay homage to the father at the place of his village.</l>
<l>She, she has many tresses [and] few bangles,</l>
<l rend="indent">	a garland that glittered [and] upright shining pure teeth, beauty spots</l>
<l rend="indent">	that budded on [her] hips with eminent bulk?, fine [and] many.</l>
<l>This village is [her] father's,</l>
<l rend="indent">	unwearyingly generous with toddy(?), with arrows in [his] strong bow,</l>
<l rend="indent2">  with broad hands, with strength in [his] neck [and] a black beard.</l>
<l>I brought her forth. May your name flourish.</l>
        </lg>
